{"version":1,"content":"<html><body><p>救援人員到場時事主昏迷不醒，隨即將他送往北區醫院搶救。警方正調查事主身份及事發經過。</p><figure><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20260318/1110941835783704576841703.jpeg/s07-Yl9OJXirDbj7TzTOlb5CSVozhLLpxRIYQcUSGEE\" alt=\"北區醫院。（資料圖片）\"><figcaption>北區醫院。（資料圖片）</figcaption></figure></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-24T00:35:48.387762+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":54,"images":1,"source":"HK01 突發","fallback":"none"}}